snippet.title: SNES Pocky & Rocky - Part 1
snippet.description:
An old classic (I think) SNES game. It was a fun game when I played it as a kid years ago. It's an odd game but it has some nice levels and interesting boss fights. 

Also the graphic is not too bad.
